Feature: Allow the user to configure two factor authentication

  Scenario: 1. Check navigation
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-nav'
    And I am on the two factor management screen with two factor 'disabled'
    When I click the setup authenticator button
    Then I arrive at the two factor enable screen

  Scenario: 2. Enable two factor
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I am on the two factor enable screen
    When I provide a valid verification code
    And I click the verify button
    Then I am on the recovery code screen

  Scenario: 3. Login with two factor
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I am on the two factor login screen
    When I provide a valid authenticator code
    And I click the log in button
    Then I am on the home screen

  Scenario: 4. Login with recovery code
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I am on the two factor login screen
    When I click the log in with recovery code button
    And I type a recovery code into the box
    And I click the recovery code submit button
    Then I am on the home screen

  Scenario: 5. Reset two factor codes (nav)
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I provide two factor information
    And I am on the two factor management screen with two factor 'enabled'
    When I click the reset recovery codes button
    Then I am on the reset recovery codes warning screen

  Scenario: 6. Reset two factor codes (perform action)
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I provide two factor information
    And I am on the two factor management screen with two factor 'enabled'
    When I click the reset recovery codes button
    And I confirm that I want to reset my recovery codes
    Then I am on the new recovery codes screen

  Scenario: 7. Remove two factor (nav)
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I provide two factor information
    And I am on the two factor management screen with two factor 'enabled'
    When I click the disable two factor button
    Then I am on the disable two factor warning screen

  Scenario: 8. Remove two factor (perform action)
    Given I am logged in as a user with id 'twofactor-enable'
    And I provide two factor information
    And I am on the two factor management screen with two factor 'enabled'
    When I click the disable two factor button
    And I confirm that I want to disable two factor
    Then I arrive at the two factor management screen with two factor 'disabled'